      private static void ReadExternalFiles.readExaminationFile(javax.swing.JList examinationList, java.util.ArrayList<Examen> arrayExamination, java.util.ArrayList<Patient> arrayPatient)
      This function extract Examen from csv file and add it to ArrayList<Examen>arrayExamination

      private static void ReadExternalFiles.readRoomFile(java.util.ArrayList<Chambre> arrayRoom, java.util.ArrayList<Examen> arrayExamination, javax.swing.JList listOfBookedRoom, javax.swing.JList switchRoomAndExaminationList)

      static void WriteInExternalFiles.writeExaminationFile(java.util.ArrayList<Examen> arrayExamination)
      This function is used for saving Examens' informations
      Each Examen stored in arrayExamination is extracted thanks to a loop The Examen's informations are saved in Examen.txt that is created at the project's root For saving those informations a toString function is override in Examen class The finally block is used to certify that the buffer has weel been closed before quitting the function
      Examen.save is only used in writing and reading Object and allow the application to switch beetween toString options this param doesn't have Getter and Setter functions to reduce all wrong using

      private static void ExaminationFunction.deleteFromArrayExamination(javax.swing.JList list, java.util.ArrayList<Examen> arrayExamination, javax.swing.JTextField patientNumberExamPanelField, javax.swing.JComboBox examinationTypeSelection, com.toedter.calendar.JDateChooser examinationDateField, javax.swing.JList switchRoomAndExaminationList, javax.swing.JList bookedList)
      this function is used to delete an Examen
      The index of the row selected in the graphic list is registered, if the result of the selected index equals -1 the function isn't executed Before deleting an Examen it is imperative to check if a Chambre has already been booked for this one If no room has been booked : - The the selected index is used to remove the Examen stored in the index of the arrayExamination - The RoomFunction.updadeExaminationListForBooking() is used
      Else if a room has been registered - The room is cloned - The RoomFunction.resetRoomDataToDefault() is put in action - The the selected index is used to remove the Examen stored in the index of the arrayExamination - The RoomFunction.updadeExaminationListForBooking() is used - The RoomFunction.printRoomInList() is used too After that the fields are cleared The updated arrayExamination is displayed in the graphic list
      private static void ExaminationFunction.deleteFromTemporaryList(javax.swing.JList list, java.util.ArrayList<Examen> arrayExamination, javax.swing.JTextField patientNumberExamPanelField, javax.swing.JComboBox examinationTypeSelection, com.toedter.calendar.JDateChooser examinationDateField, javax.swing.JList switchRoomAndExaminationList, javax.swing.JList bookedList)
      this function is used to delete an Examen
      The index of the row selected in the graphic list is registered, if the result of the selected index equals -1 the function isn't executed The Examen at the selected index is extracted of the temporaryList A loop is used to check all the Examen stored in the arrayExamination The value of all Examen are checked and to find the one selected by the user After it has been found and before deleting it, it is imperative to check if a Chambre has already been booked for this one If no room has been booked : - The selected index is used to remove the Examen stored in the index of the arrayExamination - The RoomFunction.updadeExaminationListForBooking() is used
      Else if a room has been registered - The room is cloned - The RoomFunction.resetRoomDataToDefault() is put in action - The the selected index is used to remove the Examen stored in the index of the arrayExamination - The RoomFunction.updadeExaminationListForBooking() is used - The RoomFunction.printRoomInList() is used too The Examen at the selected index is removed of the temporaryList After that the fields are cleared The updated arrayExamination is displayed in the graphic list
      private static void PatientFunction.displaySummaryList(javax.swing.JList summaryExaminationList, javax.swing.JList summaryBookingroomList, Patient patient, java.util.ArrayList<Examen> arrayExamination)
      this function is update all the Examen and Chambre related to a specific Patient
      the arraySummaryExamination and arraySummaryRoom have to be clear at the beginning of the function
      A loop is used to check all of the Examen in the arrayExamination We compare the Patient stored in the Object Examen with the one in the param of the function When the values are equals the Examen is stored in arraySummaryExamination Then an Chambre Object extract the informations related to the Chambre stored in the Examen if this Object isn't null then it is stored in arraySummaryRoom
      This process is repeted as long as we haven't reach the end of arrayExamination
      Then the results are displayed in summaryExaminationList and summaryBookingroomList
